======================================================

                     to use wd ...
       copy and source desired shell's wrapper

 wrappers in ${pkgdir}/usr/share/wd/wd{.sh|.zsh|.fish}

 example for bash:
 # mkdir ~/bin/
 # cp ${pkgdir}/usr/share/wd/wd.sh ~/bin/
 # echo \"source ~/bin/wd.sh\" >> ~/.bashrc

